trans-unit.source: Iterates over all preceding nodes according to the XPath preceding axis rules, and returns nodes in document order without duplicates.
trans-unit.target: 循环访问所有前面的节点，根据 XPath 前面的轴规则，并以没有重复项的文档顺序返回节点。

trans-unit.source: The state of the navigator changes only if the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A> method has returned `true`.
trans-unit.target: 导航器更改仅在状态<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A>方法已返回`true`。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.MoveNext%2A>

trans-unit.source: Positions the iterator on the next preceding node.
trans-unit.target: 将迭代器定位到下一步前面的节点。

trans-unit.source: If the iterator was set to the next preceding node, the MoveNext method sets the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A> property to the current result navigator; otherwise, the <xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A> property remains unchanged.
trans-unit.target: 如果迭代器已设置为下一步前面的节点，MoveNext 方法会设置<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A>属性设置为当前结果导航器; 否则为<xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A>属性保持不变。</xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A> </xref:System.Xml.Xsl.Runtime.XPathPrecedingDocOrderIterator.Current%2A>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the iterator was set to the next preceding node; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>如果迭代器设置为下一步前面的节点;否则为<xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>。
